Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear {Mr} Oreki Houtarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{formality here, can't be tld}I am currently writing to you from Benares.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although late, please accept my congratulations for passing your entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I understand, you decided upon Kamiyama High.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that you have begun high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let me give you one piece of advice as your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Join the Classics Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has a long-running history,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I too was a member during my high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have heard that the club currently has no members remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As nobody has joined this year, they plan to to disband it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As an alumnus of the club, I cannot allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Houtarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please protect the stage of your sister's youth, the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All you need to do is sign up for the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like you have anything better to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yours sincerely,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oreki Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:24.23,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Bored, sitting on the windowsill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:32.36,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}I frown at the wind to hide my awkwardness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:40.45,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,0)\blur3\t(0,989,2,\blur0.5)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:45.54,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}I nod uncertainly as I shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:51.25,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,the future in my hands feeling mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:56.42,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}I feel that the wind is bringing change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:01.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's your fault for calling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:08.60,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}The cloudy sky tells a tale of what's to come
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:17.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)}Spread our wings with more courage than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:21.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and dark are still vague in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:28.00,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,but still we want to know the reason behind kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.54,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,No one so far has ever reached
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.38,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,the shining distance far beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:44.01,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}Let's get there before the past takes it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Five, six, seven, eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been one month since the revival of the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.94,ep title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1482,473)\blur2\pos(364,554)\clip(66,556,69,599)\t(0,1482,\clip(66,556,800,599)\t(4575,5090,\clip(800,566,800,599)}Activities of the esteemed Classics Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.98,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\fax0.65\fnComfortaa\b1\c&H55656D&\blur0.7\frx16\fry12\org(851,312)\frz335.3\pos(618,304)}Earth {\fax0.6\c&H4C5459&}Sci. {\c&H3D4545&}Prep. {\fax0.55\c&H283334&}room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It ended up being much easier to visit the clubroom than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8 }Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever I'm bored after classes, I just drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought them from home.{lit presents of my home}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take whichever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as it's not too tiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't mind being around others. I'm not antisocial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a waste of time.{不毛}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean you'll save nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a stitch in time.{二毛作}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a waste of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be productive if we have no purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for those words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is there something else you expect to get out of the Classics Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a personal thing.{change reasons > matters in ep 01}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I'm talking about the club itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A club without club activities is no club at all!{部活 活動 oh how funny}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to release an anthology at the culture fair in October!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An anthology?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd take way too much {:}effort{:}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing less than an anthology will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to take part in the culture fair so badly, can't we do something easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a food stall{ or something}?{text length}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traditionally, those kinds of stalls aren't allowed at Kami High's culture fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already submitted the costings for the anthology,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our club advisor asked me to do it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Classics Club anthology is a 40-year-old tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they don't want us to just let it die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have mentioned all this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this anthology supposed to consist of, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I figured we could work that out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find one from a previous year, that might be a good starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing here.{what's with this music}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's check the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You're coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Friday, so the library assistant will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.25,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs45\fnComfortaa\pos(641,230)\c&H445E63&\b1}Library
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Oreki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see. Pity it couldn't stay that way.{lit i didn't want to meet you. very blunt}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ibara. I thought I'd {be nice and }drop by to say "hi".{line length}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sanctuary of culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not your kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet it fits {\i1}you{\i0} perfectly, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as annoying as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just came here to bother me, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you two are still getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living up to your name as Kaburaya Junior High's best couple, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it.{can it what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slug would be more fun to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... slug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Fuku, you've sure got guts to tell me that, knowing how I feel and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry. Didn't mean to reopen old wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting your jokes get the better of you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really oughta quit messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what's going on between those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's had a crush on him since junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda, this is Ibara Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the same junior high as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka, this is Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's from the Classics Club I just joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what brings you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibara, there was something I wanted to ask about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you keep the previous anthologies published by the club here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Classics Club, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Classics Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're not on the shelves, they might be in the archives...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're making a new anthology for the culture fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we thought we'd better take a look at the previous ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're doing something for the Kan'ya Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised Houtarou agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda happened after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the "Kan'ya Fair"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what everyone calls Kamiyama High's culture fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't another of your tall tales, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! My seniors in the Handicraft Club all call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it that in the Book Club too.{sup 8th}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kan'ya"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... though I asked around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably started off as the "Kamiyama High School Culture Fair",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then became the "Kamiyama Culture Fair",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the "Kan'yama Fair" and finally the "Kan'ya Fair", I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chitanda,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we might be able to find them if we take a look in the archives,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the librarian is at a staff meeting right now, so we can't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be back in about half an hour, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we could wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} might as well go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka, why don't you tell them that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Eh?}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,feel like putting your brain to work for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The popular but unwanted book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The popular but unwanted book?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty weird story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard we thought, it never made any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka and I were out of ideas.{it had us baffled}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every Friday, I'm here working as the assistant librarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And every Friday I see the same book in the returns tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For five weeks in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird enough on its own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.96,book,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.8\frz180\frx40\fry0\pos(632,229)}kamiyama high school: \Nfifty years of history
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a peek inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just your typical school history book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look like an easy read.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be that unusual for someone to borrow this every week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never borrowed a book from here, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow books for up to two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wouldn't need to keep borrowing the same book every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, this book gets returned every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who keeps borrowing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The list of borrowers is at the back. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.68,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\fs40\fnCentury\c&HCACEA7&\pos(207,96)\frz8.726}Class
