Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.68,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\fs40\fnCentury\c&HD3D7B5&\frz9.904\pos(838,-20)}Borrowed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.68,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\frz8.373\pos(486,142)}Suzuki Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.68,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\frz8.373\pos(593,215)}Shima Saori
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.68,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.6\frz8.373\pos(721,287)}Yamaguchi\N Ryouko
