Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.68,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.6\frz10.65\pos(742,480)}Machita\N Kyouko
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A different person borrows it every week! And they all return it on the same day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:27.18,replay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.2\pos(147,671)}{TS 1020}{bottom left corner}Replay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.68,0:10:27.18,replay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1014,666)\alpha&HFF&\blur3}IV. XX, {\t(3276,3860,\alpha&H00&\blur1.2)}15:40
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:27.18,replay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.2\pos(1014,666)}IV. XX, {\t(3276,3860,\alpha&HFF&\blur3)}12:21
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all borrowed and returned it on the same day, for five weeks in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also know when it was borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They always borrow it during lunch break and return it after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught your interest?{obviously they have some local history class}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.70,book,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\fs45\blur0.8\frz351\frx346\fry350\org(575,561)\c&HE0EBE2&\pos(385,606)}kamiyama high school: \Nfifty years of history
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just consider it for a moment, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pretty interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You figured out the story behind the locked door and the secret club so easily too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just an interesting side of Houtarou that you may not have heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out. It sounds bad when you say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to say no at this point would cost me significantly more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. Let's mull it over for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuku, was Oreki actually smart all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with pointless{yaku ni tatanai} stuff like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every now and then he's not entirely useless.{yaku ni tatsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can shut up now.
