Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For five weeks in a row, different people have borrowed this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and returned it on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be easy to say it's a coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Chitanda wouldn't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't have to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It just has to be something Chitanda can accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see.
