Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They didn't borrow the book because they wanted to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do with a book besides reading it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could put a few books together to use as a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could tie it to your arm and use it as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put some effort into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There has to be some purpose that only this book could be used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you think, Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could use it to flatten vegetables for pickling!{really}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of honor roll did she manage to end up on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The local district's "Top Airheads"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look at this from another angle.
