Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we conclude from the fact that someone different borrows it each week?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at their names, they're all girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of two possibilities.
