Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:15.31,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H727E8A&\pos(186,62)\fad(50,150)}Someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, that they have nothing in common,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this book is just popular on Friday afternoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that they use the book as a group,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.48,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H727E8A&\pos(197,282)\fad(50,50)}Machita \NKyouko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.48,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H6D7581&\pos(386,107)\fad(50,50)}Sawakiguchi Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.48,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H6D7581&\pos(582,142)\fad(50,50)}Tori Saori
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.48,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H6D7581&\pos(524,318)\fad(50,50)}Suzuki Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.48,names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H6D7581&\pos(352,286)\fad(50,50)}Yamaguchi \NRyouko {the round thing is the same as before}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and borrow it in turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.48,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\xshad-2\fad(229,0)\pos(634,288)\fnEdo SZ\b1\c&H202423&\4c&H6C7F8E&}No group         Group
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about for fortune-telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your lucky item this week is... the school history book!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you borrow it Friday afternoon and return it the same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything will go well with your boyfriend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. And remember, this happened five weeks in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.{lit I just said it (no reason).}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what they have in common: They're all second-year girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Different classes, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a reason they're all girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you randomly selected five students from this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a decent chance they'll all be girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls{he says it gender neutral} like to stick together too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be some kind of secret message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like returning it one way up to say you passed, and the other way up to say you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they could use it as a message in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really tell which way up they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess no matter how much Oreki thinks about it, that's as far as he can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuku spent ages thinking about it as... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't smell anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite pungent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like paint thinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a dog...{fucking rofl}{sure is acchi kocchi in here}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if Chitanda is so certain about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she could be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou, your face says you figured something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of. I can't be certain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda, how about a bit of exercise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this place I'd like you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not going. Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him just make you run around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can only be useful if someone uses {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know when to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just thought that if I needed to go somewhere you'd want come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for honoring our restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have prepared two menus for you.
