Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chef's suggestion is this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PE class had to be called off today due to rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I still have some energy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how limited is your energy to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuku, can you take the counter for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave when I'm supposed to be minding the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold the fort while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where are we going, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The art room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's in the other building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any limit to your laziness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's in the art room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, let's organize our information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider what they would use the book for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I doubt there are any girls who would use that huge book during their break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means they must use it in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering that they're in the same year but different classes, what subjects could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PE or arts classes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The five girls took turns borrowing the book before class every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know if it's every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since books can be borrowed for up to two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so huge, it'd be easier to just borrow it again each week than to take it home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells like the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look inside and you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they use the book for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Classes 2-D, 2-E and 2-F take Art together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they would have painted those pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The book's cover makes it perfect as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that smell was paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a moment of inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.24,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs45\fnComfortaa\pos(641,230)\b1\c&H3B6876&}Library
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well done, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought they'd use it as a model for painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you manage to figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as average as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really did surprise me, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really interested in what goes on inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much I'd like to cut it open to see.{gtfo sylar}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing unusual about my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A top-ranking student like yourself wouldn't get anything out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The midterms are still a while away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure she'll be among the best in our year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I get good grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just putting together things I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to know is beyond those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to understand the system that gives birth to thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, her sense of smell is even more of a mystery to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Oreki could...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that was pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It was loads of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was all over so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent hours on it and never figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said he can be useful at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I hate being outdone by Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really, really frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now, chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This just isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rare flash of sparkling brilliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oreki, you can't leave yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. The anthology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We need to wait for the librarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, Houtarou acts like he's not all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibara, thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're back, Ms. Itoigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fukube Satoshi from the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for an old edition of the anthology to refer to when making the new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we take a look in the archives?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Classics Club's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anthology?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the Classics Club? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but we don't have any of the previous anthologies in the archive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you have overlooked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so. If we had it, I'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find it, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel refreshed from having solved that mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do about it. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still had a good harvest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a personal thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Oreki could...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Oreki speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? It's Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, were you resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was my sister calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? How come you're calling on a Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to meet you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.77,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fnHand Of Sean\c&H4B7E78&\fs30\pos(771,169)\frz9.098\frx14\fry342}Pine\Napple \NSand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask a very special favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking why you had me come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who chose this café.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Sundays are important to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to waste my time on this comedy act!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nervous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you planning to confess to me or something?{yfw}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might consider it a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:10.51,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)\blur2}Let us meet in a blissful dream tonight, let it be our love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:14.51,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur2}Find me, I beg you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:19.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,350)\blur2}We promised to meet, drifting in and out of sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.03,0:24:40.75,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur2}This sprouting warmth confuses us
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.83,0:24:51.67,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2}Don't you understand this feeling yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:24:57.76,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2}Normally such random glances hold no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.76,0:25:03.10,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,450)\blur2}Isn't it the same when making friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:08.86,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2}The little shooting stars we wish upon, vanishing into the dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.86,0:25:13.82,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2}are a magic that only unfolds in the night
